User Management

Users

User management is handled through Keycloak. Use the Keycloak Admin Console to manage users, roles, and permissions.

Keycloak Integration

Keycloak URL

http://localhost:8080

Realm

master

Admin Credentials

admin / admin123

Open Keycloak Admin Console

User Management Guide

  • Create User: Go to Users → Add User → Fill details → Save
  • Assign Roles: Go to User → Role Mappings → Assign realm roles
  • Reset Password: Go to User → Credentials → Reset Password
  • Enable/Disable: Go to User → Settings → Toggle Enabled
  • View Sessions: Go to User → Sessions

Available Roles

user admin super_admin
